drove me nutsfor the longest time.  the spring fits into the slot in the
keeper blocks for the rocker arm.s and the slot faces down.  so yes it is
under the bolts, all 4 of them, and is held by the slot in the block of
steel that holds the rocker arm assembly..  only takes 6 hands to install


